[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "結局、昨日は帰ってこなかったわね。\n夜食を差し入れに行ったら、まだ唸ってたし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00227",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様ならきっと、何か思いつくはず……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00228",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ただいまーっと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00229",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "あら、おかえりなさい。いい案は出たの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00230",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "思いっきり追い詰められたら意外と出るもんね。\nアルビちゃんの新境地、ようやっと拓けたり！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00231",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ずーっとぼんやりは見えてたんだけど、ようやく\nくっきり見え申した",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00232",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まあ、この発想を実現するためには\n新しい装備を調合しなくちゃいけないんだけどね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00233",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "徹夜でクマができた姉様も素敵",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00234",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "もう、ベップは何があっても素敵なんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00235",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "そんな姉様に贈りものがあるの。\nこれ、どうぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00236",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "どうしたのこれ！　こんなにたくさんの素材！\nしかもどれも貴重な、ちょうどアタシが欲してたやつ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00237",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "それはレスナが用意したもの……\n姉様の決意が固まったら渡してあげて、って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00238",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんと……アタシが立ち直って、必要になるものも\n予期していたとは……さすがレスナパイセン……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00239",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "錬金術のことはよく分からないけれど、\n見る限り原材料って感じの素材が多いわね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00240",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん、大元の素材だけよこして、\nここからさらに調合を重ねる必要がある……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00241",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "錬金術士であれば、自らが求めるものは\n自分で作り出せ、ってことだと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00242",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "っていうかアルビーナならこれくらいできるよね？\nっていう先輩からの挑戦状、かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00243",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "先輩からの、重い愛ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00244",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うっす、あざーっす！\nこの愛、応えてみせやしょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00245",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "足りない素材を集めに、いざ、しゅっぱーつ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00246",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "アルビーナ、ちょっと寝といたほうがいいんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00247",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "一段落したら一緒に寝ましょうね、姉様",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00248",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]